ca.ualberta.cs.wrkify

Class BidViewHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.ViewHolder
      • ca.ualberta.cs.wrkify.BidViewHolder

  • public class BidViewHolder
extends android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.ViewHolder
    Used by BidListAdapter. Holds Views in the inflated layout representing a Bid item. Handles setting of Bid data given a Bid Handles collapse/expand by hiding/showing Views, though does not animate them Hides accept/reject buttons when necessary
    See Also:
    BidListAdapter
